msgstr "**空ジオメトリも削除する**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5543
msgid "``REMOVE_EMPTY``"
msgstr "``REMOVE_EMPTY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5546
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5591
msgid "**Non null geometries**"
msgstr "**NULLジオメトリでない地物の出力レイヤ**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5561
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5587
msgid "**Null geometries**"
msgstr "**NULLジオメトリの出力レイヤ**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5564
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5588
msgid "``NULL_OUTPUT``"
msgstr "``NULL_OUTPUT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5567
msgid "Default: ``[Skip output]``"
msgstr "デフォルト： ``[出力をスキップ]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5590
msgid "Output vector layer (for NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr "（NULLジオメトリの、オプションを選択した場合には空ジオメトリも含む）出力ベクタレイヤ"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5594
msgid ""
"The output vector layer (without NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr "（NULLジオメトリではない、かつオプションを選択した場合には空ジオメトリでもない）出力ベクタレイヤ"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5599
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:removenullgeometries``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:removenullgeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5609
msgid "Reverse line direction"
msgstr "線の向きの反転"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5610
msgid "Inverts the direction of a line layer."
msgstr "ラインレイヤの向きを反転します。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5615
msgid "Before and after the direction inversion"
msgstr "線の向きの反転前と反転後"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5636
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5660
msgid "**Reversed**"
msgstr "**出力レイヤ**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5663
msgid "The output line vector layer (with reversed lines)"
msgstr "（線の向きが反転した）出力ラインベクタレイヤ"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5668
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:reverselinedirection``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:reverselinedirection``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5678
msgid "Rotate"
msgstr "ジオメトリの回転"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5679
msgid ""
"Rotates feature geometries by the specified angle clockwise. The rotation "
"occurs around each feature's centroid, or optionally around a unique preset "
"point."
msgstr ""
"地物ジオメトリを指定された角度だけ時計回りに回転させます。回転は各地物の重心を中心に行われますが、オプションとして指定した単一の点を中心に回転させることもできます。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5687
msgid ":ref:`qgistranslategeometry`, :ref:`qgisswapxy`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgistranslategeometry`, :ref:`qgisswapxy`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5705
msgid "**Rotation (degrees clockwise)**"
msgstr "**回転する角度（時計回り、単位は度）**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5710
msgid "Angle of the rotation in degrees"
msgstr "度単位で表した回転角度"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5711
msgid "**Rotation anchor point (x, y)**"
msgstr "**回転の中心**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5714
msgid "``ANCHOR``"
msgstr "``ANCHOR``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5715
msgid "[coordinates]"
msgstr "[座標]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5718
msgid ""
"X,Y coordinates of the point to rotate the features around. If not set the "
"rotation occurs around each feature's centroid."
msgstr "地物の回転中心となる点のXY座標。指定されていない場合は、各地物の重心の周りに回転します。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5722
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5746
msgid "**Rotated**"
msgstr "**出力レイヤ**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5749
msgid "The output vector layer with rotated geometries"
msgstr "回転したジオメトリの出力ベクタレイヤ"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5754
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rotatefeatures``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rotatefeatures``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5764
msgid "Roundness"
msgstr "丸み係数"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5768
msgid ""
"The roundness of a polygon is defined as 4π × polygon area / perimeter². The"
" roundness value varies between 0 and 1. A perfect circle has a roundness of"
" 1, while a completely flat polygon has a roundness of 0."
msgstr ""
"ポリゴンの丸み係数は、4π × ポリゴンの面積 / 周囲長² "
"と定義されます。丸み係数の値は0と1の間です。完全な円の丸み係数は1で、完全に平らなポリゴンの丸み係数は0です。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5772
msgid "The algorithm returns NULL for multipart polygon features."
msgstr "アルゴリズムはマルチパートポリゴン地物にNULLを返します。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5795
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5819
msgid "**Roundness**"
msgstr "**丸み係数**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5827
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:roundness``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:roundness``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5837
msgid "Segmentize by maximum angle"
msgstr "曲線のセグメント化（角度）"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5838
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5916
msgid ""
"Segmentizes a geometry by converting curved sections to linear sections."
msgstr "曲線部分を直線化することで、ジオメトリをセグメント化します。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5841
msgid ""
"The segmentization is performed by specifying the maximum allowed radius "
"angle between vertices on the straightened geometry (e.g the angle of the "
"arc created from the original arc center to consecutive output vertices on "
"the linearized geometry). Non-curved geometries will be retained without "
"change."
msgstr ""
"セグメント化は、直線化されるジオメトリ上の頂点間の最大許容半径角度（元の円弧の曲率中心と、直線化されたジオメトリ上の連続する出力頂点がなす角度）を指定することによって実行されます。湾曲していないジオメトリはそのまま、変更されません。"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5847
msgid ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance` 、 :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries` 、 "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5866
msgid "**Maximum angle between vertices (degrees)**"
msgstr "**セグメントの最大許容角度（単位は度）**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5870
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7301
msgid "Default: 5.0"
msgstr "デフォルト： 5.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5871
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed radius angle between vertices on the straightened geometry"
msgstr "直線化されたジオメトリ上の頂点間の最大許容中心角"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5873
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5897
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5951
